flowRoot.flowPara: Frequent double archetype in US Movies: married couple, who live a life in luxury financed with robbery and murder, including massive drug abuse. Often described as an "idyllic" partnership. These roless or archetypes seem to be protected by the CIA as the USA Gouvernment seems to use them as startegic chessman / -combination in an occupation country (imperialism). Abusing the "family is the basic unit of our society ..." from the human rights shameless and the children of the couple often suffer and have to pay the bill later. Beeing protected by a system as big as the CIA means, that they will become ignorant after a short while.

The role of the judge is one of the most powerful in the system, in many movies shown as a fat "cute" Santa Claus. The role would be perfect for a mastermind of a terror-network to hide in such a role that is hardly ever shown as the evil killer in TV. In computer science one would speak of a single point of failure, so it would also be perfect for a foreign aggressor, secret service to subdue the whole system.
